no business here, please leave.

Azel: Please don't push yourself too
hard. After it's finished, let's have a
celebration with everyone.
Knight: Ah!! Y-Yes! I'll gladly do it!!
Zerachiel: Wow, you look so happy.
Claudia: It feels like that, doesn't it?

Azel: I'm not very good with those kinds
of emotions, so Aries often scolded
me...

Knight: Thank you very much. The Magic
Continent was saved from destruction,
all thanks to all of you.

Zerachiel: I never expected to be
thanked this much...

Knight: I'm sorry, but it's not open to
the public. If it's just the exterior,
feel free to take a look as much as you
want.

Unie, you are very welcome.
